description.en-us: Track Stars Haulers was the first series of transport trucks that do not include a bonus vehicle. The series was introduced in 2014, and similar to Trackin' Trucks , these noticeably smaller than other series transporters, which allowed them to run on tracks. Also in 2014, Super Rigs was launched, which returned to the sizing of previous series and retained the bonus vehicle. The line was renamed to Track Fleet in 2024.
